{With 15 points and four of partner's suit you naturally bid 2NT. Partner now jumps to 4\H.  

Partner's rebid of 4\H is not strong. He is using the Principle of Fast Arrival to indicate a minimum opening hand. Since you have nothing extra you pass quietly.}

